canonical:
  title: 花山上元文機障子
  author: 洪功佐
  language: lzh
  text: 率滸西來徙邑岐花山新長萬年枝八仙鵠嶺微茫遠三島鼇峯怳惚移風遞玉簫過海送月和蓮燭傍簾窺都人士女顔如織猶勝康安曲宴時
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 花山上元文機障子
  author: 洪功佐
  language: lzh
  text: 率滸西來徙邑岐。花山新長萬年枝。八仙鵠嶺微茫遠。三島鼇峯怳惚移。風遞玉簫過海送。月和蓮燭傍簾窺。都人士女顔如織。猶勝康安曲宴時。
korean:
  title: 화산 상원 문기장자
  author: 홍공좌
  language: kor
  text: |-
    서호를 따라와 기산에 옮았으니
    화산에 새로 만년지가 자랐네
    여덟 신선 사는 곡령(8신선(神仙)이 사는 곳)은 아득히 멀어도
    세 섬 자라봉은 황홀히 옮겨 온 듯
    바람결에 신선의 옥피리를 바다 건너 보내 오고
    달은 연촉과 어울려 발로 엿보누나
    온 도성 사녀들의 얼굴들이 베짠 듯 빽빽하니
    강안전 잔치 때보다 오히려 더 낫구나
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0170_010_0290&viewSync=OT
  footnotes:
  - key: '[주-D001] 서호(西滸)를 …… 옮았으니 : '
    value: 주(周)의 선조가, “서쪽 물가를 따라 부족을 거느리고 기산(岐山)으로 옮아왔다[率滸西來].” 여기는 개경(開京)에서부터 강화(江華)로 도읍을 옮겼음을 뜻한다.
english:
  title: 'On the Lantern Festival at Flower Mountain: A Screen with Embroidered Themes'
  author: Hong Gong-jwa
  language: eng
  text: |-
    Following the western waters, the capital moves to Kia's mountain.
    On Flower Mountain, the thousand-year boughs now newly flourish.
    The Cranes' Ridge where the Eight Immortals dwell grows distant and dim,
    Yet the Three Islands' Tortoise Peak seems to drift before us, ethereal.
    On the wind, a celestial jade flute carries its song across the sea,
    And moonlight mingles with lotus candles, glimpsed through the curtain's edge.
    The faces of the city's daughters and sons weave together thick as cloth—
    A throng that surpasses even the grand banquets of Kangaan's day.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: The poem commemorates the relocation of the capital from Gae-gyeong to Ganghwa during the Goryeo period, using the classical allusion of the Zhou ancestors moving westward to the foot of Mount Kia.
  - key: ''
    value: The Eight Immortals and Three Islands reference Daoist paradises, suggesting the transformed landscape has taken on an otherworldly beauty.
  - key: ''
    value: Kangaan (康安) refers to a celebrated ancient festival known for its elegant gatherings and entertainment.
